defaultthat the 
defaultGovernment believes could play a significant role in 
defaultlow carbon 
defaultelectricity 
defaultgener
defaulta
defaulttion
default.
default Many Governments share this view 
defaultand 
defaultthe UK is regarded as amongst the most supportive internationally.
