defaultthe term instead covers several types of similar technologies 
defaultused in each part of t
defaulthe 
defaultCCS Chain
default.  T
defaulthe main variations being in the area of capture technologies which can be tailored to suit the application. Fo
defaultr example, in the power sector
default 
