default and commercial risks around novel business structures. 
default24.
default&#xa0; 
defaultThe novelty of integration and scaling up means that first-of-a-kind full chain CCS projects 
defaultface significant barriers to investment 
defaultand CCS is 
defaultnot yet cost-competitive with other low carbon technologies
default. Initial projects have high
defaulter
default capture costs and ener
defaultgy penalties. Building the first transportation infrastructure and proving the first CO2 stores is 
defaultcapital intensive
default. 
