defaultThe Government also recognises the importance 
defaulto
defaultf long term regulatory and price signals for investor certainty. For this reason we have brought forward a ‘triple lock’ of 
defaultpolicies designed to encourage deployment of CCS. These are (i) the National Policy Statement for Energy’s Carbon Capture Readiness 
defaultrequirements, and stipulation that there should be no new coal power plants over 300MW built without CCS
